OL,3,CFrench households to receive 'survival
OL,4,Cmanual' to prepare for emergencies
OL,6,FEvery household in France will receive
OL,7,Fa 20-page "survival manual" to help
OL,8,Fpeople prepare for "imminent threats",
OL,9,Faccording to a government spokesperson.
OL,11,FThe manual will include guidance on
OL,12,Fwhat to do in natural disasters,
OL,13,Ftechnological and cyber incidents,
OL,14,Fhealth crises such as a pandemic and
OL,15,Fsecurity crises, including terrorist
OL,16,Fattacks and armed conflict, the
OL,17,Fspokeswoman for Prime Minister
OL,18,FFrancois Bayrou told ITV News' US
OL,19,Fpartner CNN.
