OL,3,CFrench households to receive 'survival
OL,4,Cmanual' to prepare for emergencies
OL,6,FThe content is expected to be similar
OL,7,Fto information launched online by the
OL,8,FFrench government in 2022, which
OL,9,Fadvises on what to do in an emergency.
OL,11,FAmong the recommendations will be
OL,12,Fhaving a list of contacts for the
OL,13,Femergency services, knowing which
OL,14,Fradio channels to tune into, and
OL,15,Fensuring that all doors are shut in
OL,16,Fthe event of a nuclear accident.
