OL,3,CFrench households to receive 'survival
OL,4,Cmanual' to prepare for emergencies
OL,6,FThe manual will also outline ways to
OL,7,Fcontribute to the defence of the
OL,8,Fcommunity, including volunteering for
OL,9,Freserve units or local firefighting
OL,10,Fgroups.
OL,12,FSweden and Finland have recently
OL,13,Fupdated similar booklets distributed
OL,14,Fto citizens to include instructions on
OL,15,Fpreparing for communications outages,
OL,16,Fpower cuts and extreme weather events.
