OL,3,CFrench households to receive 'survival
OL,4,Cmanual' to prepare for emergencies
OL,6,FEach household is also recommended to
OL,7,Fprepare a "survival kit", which should
OL,8,Finclude six litres of bottled water, a
OL,9,Fdozen tins of food, batteries and a
OL,10,Ftorch in case of power outages.
OL,12,FPeople are also advised to buy medical
OL,13,Fsupplies such as paracetamol,
OL,14,Fcompresses and saline solution.
OL,16,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,17,Fensure citizens are ready to respond
OL,18,Fin the event of a crisis," the
OL,19,Fgovernment spokesperson said.
