OL,6,FThe announcement comes after a major
OL,7,Foverhaul to France's security forces,
OL,8,Fwhich was announced by President
OL,9,FEmmanuel Macron earlier this month.
OL,11,FIt includes plans to increase the
OL,12,Fnumber of operational reservists from
OL,13,F40,000 to 100,000 by 2035.
OL,15,F"Our country and our continent must
OL,16,Fcontinue to defend themselves, equip
OL,17,Fthemselves, and prepare if we want to
OL,18,Favoid war," Macron said at a military
OL,19,Fbase on Tuesday.
